{
  "stem": "11882.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He had just petted the little kitty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, charmed with it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I thought, my golly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was-- I was-- I was scared to death, because I had also the responsibility of this little kid.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I understood that they thought we were Jews, and we were doing something wrong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We were petting the kitty, and that much I grasped.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So we hurried home, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We didn't go walking anymore in that area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And you will be glad to know the family all managed to get to America in 1938.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they got along.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I-- I don't suppose they acquired very much money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They're in South Carolina now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Some of them, unfortunately, I read about their deaths in an story, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "The dear woman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She studied then, when she got to America, right away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "They all were very eager to study, very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She learned to be a practical nurse.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And there she was very good, a lovely personality.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the children went to school, I guess in New York at first.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then they must have settled in Charleston, South Carolina.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And the little boy grew up and went to the Navy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My story?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was rather meager because there was no job, even now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went to work for the Gallup Poll and things like that to at least get something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in different stores, the bookkeeping-- bookkeeping department or something and never did get a teaching job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But suddenly, Adolf Hitler, who managed our history and my history, too.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Started our war or got us afraid of war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was 1940-- I got back in autumn 1939.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we got into the war in December of '41.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And before that, the government started recruiting us government girls.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
